@{b}Spike Soldier@{ub}

Color   = Green
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Summon Spike (0/0)
Cost    = 2GG
Artist  = Randy Elliott

Text(SH): Spike Soldier comes into play with three +1/+1 counters on it.
          <2>, Remove a +1/+1 counter from Spike Soldier: Put a +1/+1 counter
          on target creature.
          Remove a +1/+1 counter from Spike Soldier: Spike Soldier gets
